    "epitet": "Dark One",
    "description": "A wily mage who serves Gangrel of Plegia. Excels at using her charms to disarm and then destroy her foes. Appears in Fire Emblem Awakening.",
    "artist": "PenekoR (п猫Ｒ)",
    "voiceActorEN": "Cindy Robinson",
    "voiceActorJP": "たなか久美",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "Please, call me Aversa. My, you're adorable. If you don't watch out, I'll tease you mercilessly.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "No one in this country knows me. Nor do they know what I have done. I find that strangely comforting. Heh-heh.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "You know, it's quite impudent of you to ask about my past. Oh, look at you! I'm just kidding. Hee-hee!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "No matter what world you find yourself in, chores don't do themselves. I'll do my share.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I've been told there is a nearby waterfall. I do love them... Come, give chase. We shall make a splash!",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "Are you to serve as my guard? I assure you—I am trustworthy. I was just tending to my injuries.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I am Aversa. I bring you a small token of affection—not mine, of course.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "All the naughty children who get in my way will quake with terror.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Playtime is just about over... Get ready for something new.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "What a scary face! We should be enjoying ourselves...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "Is this what you've been wanting?",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "You come all the way out here rather often, don't you? I guess you don't trust me. I'm not a spy, you know. That's not it? You think I look sad? You don't miss much, do you? It's true. I have many regrets. I've done terrible things to a lot of people. There is no way I can atone for it all... My past clings to me. No matter what I do, I can't make peace with it. And whenever I try to speak with others, well...it gets in the way. Speak plainly, you say? As if that'd ever work. If you're that interested in me, why don't we spend a little time together? Until moonrise, perhaps? As you may have noticed, I'm the fiercely loyal type.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
